005package edu.wpi.first.hal.simulation;
006
007import edu.wpi.first.hal.JNIWrapper;
008
009/** JNI for analog gyro data. */
010public class AnalogGyroDataJNI extends JNIWrapper {
011  public static native int registerAngleCallback(
012      int index, NotifyCallback callback, boolean initialNotify);
013
014  public static native void cancelAngleCallback(int index, int uid);
015
016  public static native double getAngle(int index);
017
018  public static native void setAngle(int index, double angle);
019
020  public static native int registerRateCallback(
021      int index, NotifyCallback callback, boolean initialNotify);
022
023  public static native void cancelRateCallback(int index, int uid);
024
025  public static native double getRate(int index);
026
027  public static native void setRate(int index, double rate);
028
029  public static native int registerInitializedCallback(
030      int index, NotifyCallback callback, boolean initialNotify);
031
032  public static native void cancelInitializedCallback(int index, int uid);
033
034  public static native boolean getInitialized(int index);
035
036  public static native void setInitialized(int index, boolean initialized);
037
038  public static native void resetData(int index);
039
040  /** Utility class. */
041  private AnalogGyroDataJNI() {}
042}
